pageContext.description: Socketed celt with side carrying loop cracked, and part of side missing. Corrosion has raise a knob immediately in centre of one face under rim of socket, but this does not occur on other side. No decoration. C. Square ended socket, 1.1" x 1.2"
pageContext.other: Length: 3.5" = 88.9mm,Width: 1.7" outside edge of loop to outside of socket = 43.18mm; 1.4" cutting edge = 35.56mm
pageContext.associations: The rest of the hoard is in County Record Office, Chelmsford, except for socketed celt 721/2
pageContext.toSearch: Vange, Basildon, Basildon, Essex Ss16, UK
